description: Try our easy to follow Barramundi Burger recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Barramundi Burger Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Halve each roll and spread both sides with hummus. Place lettuce, beetroot, tomato, pineapple and barramundi on one half of each roll. Top with remaining roll halves. Serve burgers with rainbow coleslaw on the side.
